sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant HB as heartbeat_service
    participant DS as dispatch_service
    participant AR as agent_router
    participant TH as Task Hub (SQLite)
    participant SIM as Simone (Claude Code)
    participant VP as VP / Cody

    HB->>DS: dispatch_sweep()
    DS->>TH: claim_next_dispatch_tasks(limit=N)
    TH-->>DS: [task_ids in_progress]
    DS->>AR: route_all_to_simone(task_ids)
    AR->>SIM: heartbeat injection with batch context
    SIM->>SIM: triage in-context
    alt simple / answerable
        SIM->>TH: mark task completed (with completion_token)
    else needs specialist
        SIM->>TH: mark task delegated
        TH->>VP: claim delegated task
        VP-->>TH: mission finished → pending_review
        SIM->>SIM: next heartbeat sweep
        SIM->>TH: sign off → completed
    else needs human
        SIM->>TH: mark task needs_review
        SIM->>SIM: draft email reply (AgentMail)
    end
